{"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"DBusObjectManagerClientRef","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"title":"DBusObjectManagerClientRef","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"DBusObjectManagerClientRef","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"struct","roleHeading":"Structure","externalID":"s:3GIO26DBusObjectManagerClientRefV"},"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Initializers","generated":true,"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef\/init(_:)-520vh","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef\/init(_:)-5mvyn","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef\/init(_:)-6rbo0","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef\/init(_:)-8drxr","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef\/init(_:)-9bds7","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef\/init(cPointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef\/init(constPointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef\/init(gconstpointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef\/init(gpointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef\/init(mutating:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef\/init(opaquePointer:)"]},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef\/ptr"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties","generated":true,"title":"Instance Properties"},{"anchor":"Type-Methods","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef\/unowned(_:)"],"title":"Type Methods"},{"anchor":"Default-Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef\/AsyncInitableProtocol-Implementations","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef\/DBusObjectManagerClientProtocol-Implementations","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef\/DBusObjectManagerProtocol-Implementations","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef\/GWeakCapturing-Implementations","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef\/InitableProtocol-Implementations","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef\/ObjectProtocol-Implementations"],"generated":true,"title":"Default Implementations"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/dbusobjectmanagerclientref"]}],"kind":"symbol","relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/AsyncInitableProtocol","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientProtocol","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerProtocol","doc:\/\/GIO\/4GLib14PointerWrapperP","doc:\/\/GIO\/10GLibObject14GWeakCapturingP","doc:\/\/GIO\/10GLibObject0B8ProtocolP","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/InitableProtocol"],"type":"conformsTo"}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDBusObjectManagerClient"},{"text":" is used to create, monitor and delete object","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"proxies for remote objects exported by a [class","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerServer","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"]"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"(or any code implementing the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"http:\/\/dbus.freedesktop.org\/doc\/dbus-specification.html#standard-interfaces-objectmanager"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"interface)."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"DBusObjectManagerClientRef"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Once an instance of this type has been created, you can connect to"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the [signal[DBusObjectManager](\/\/documentation\/gio\/dbusobjectmanager\/onobjectadded(flags:handler:)] and"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"[signal[DBusObjectManager](\/\/documentation\/gio\/dbusobjectmanager\/onobjectremoved(flags:handler:) signals] and inspect the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"[class","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectProxy"},{"text":"] objects returned by","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"[method","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.DBusObjectManager.get_objects"},{"text":"].","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the name for a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDBusObjectManagerClient"},{"text":" is not owned by anyone at","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"object construction time, the default behavior is to request the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"message bus to launch an owner for the name. This behavior can be"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"disabled using the ","type":"text"},{"code":"G_DBUS_OBJECT_MANAGER_CLIENT_FLAGS_DO_NOT_AUTO_START","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"flag. It’s also worth noting that this only works if the name of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"interest is activatable in the first place. E.g. in some cases it","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is not possible to launch an owner for the requested name. In this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"case, "},{"code":"GDBusObjectManagerClient","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" object construction still succeeds but","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"there will be no object proxies","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"(e.g. [method","type":"text"},{"code":"Gio.DBusObjectManager.get_objects","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"] returns the empty list) and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the [property"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClient"},{"type":"text","text":"] property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NULL"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The owner of the requested name can come and go (for example","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"consider a system service being restarted) – "},{"code":"GDBusObjectManagerClient","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"handles this case too; simply connect to the [signal[Object](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/object\/onnotify(flags:handler:)]","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"signal to watch for changes on the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[property"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClient","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":"] property. When the name","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"owner vanishes, the behavior is that","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"[property","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClient"},{"type":"text","text":"] is set to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NULL"},{"text":" (this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"includes emission of the [signal[Object](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/object\/onnotify(flags:handler:)] signal) and then"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"[signal[DBusObjectManager](\/\/documentation\/gio\/dbusobjectmanager\/onobjectremoved(flags:handler:)] signals are synthesized","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for all currently existing object proxies. Since"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"[property","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClient","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"] is "},{"code":"NULL","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" when this"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"happens, you can use this information to disambiguate a synthesized signal"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"from a genuine signal caused by object removal on the remote","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"[iface","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManager","isActive":true},{"text":"]. Similarly, when a new name owner appears,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[signal[DBusObjectManager](\/\/documentation\/gio\/dbusobjectmanager\/onobjectadded(flags:handler:)] signals are synthesized"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"while [property","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClient","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"] is still "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NULL"},{"type":"text","text":". Only"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"when all object proxies have been added, the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"[property","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClient","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"] is set to the new name"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"owner (this includes emission of the [signal[Object](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/object\/onnotify(flags:handler:)] signal).","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Furthermore, you are guaranteed that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[property"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClient","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"] will alternate between a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"name owner (e.g. "},{"code":":1.42","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":") and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NULL"},{"text":" even in the case where","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the name of interest is atomically replaced","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Ultimately, ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDBusObjectManagerClient"},{"type":"text","text":" is used to obtain"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"[class","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusProxy","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":"] instances. All signals (including the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"org.freedesktop.DBus.Properties"},{"type":"text","text":"PropertiesChanged"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":" signal) delivered to [class"},{"type":"text","text":"DBusProxy``] instances are guaranteed to originate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"from the name owner. This guarantee along with the behavior"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"described above, means that certain race conditions including the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"“half the proxy is from the old owner and the other half is from"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the new owner” problem cannot happen."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To avoid having the application connect to signals on the returned","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"[class","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectProxy","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":"] and [class","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusProxy","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"] objects, the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[signal[DBusObject](\/\/documentation\/gio\/dbusobject\/oninterfaceadded(flags:handler:)],"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[signal[DBusObject](\/\/documentation\/gio\/dbusobject\/oninterfaceremoved(flags:handler:)],"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[signal[DBusProxy](\/\/documentation\/gio\/dbusproxy\/ongpropertieschanged(flags:handler:)] and"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[signal[DBusProxy](\/\/documentation\/gio\/dbusproxy\/ongsignal(flags:handler:)] signals"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"are also emitted on the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDBusObjectManagerClient"},{"text":" instance managing these","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects. The signals emitted are"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[signal[DBusObjectManager](\/\/documentation\/gio\/dbusobjectmanager\/oninterfaceadded(flags:handler:)],"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[signal[DBusObjectManager](\/\/documentation\/gio\/dbusobjectmanager\/oninterfaceremoved(flags:handler:)],"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"[signal[DBusObjectManagerClient](\/\/documentation\/gio\/dbusobjectmanagerclient\/oninterfaceproxypropertieschanged(flags:handler:)] and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[signal[DBusObjectManagerClient](\/\/documentation\/gio\/dbusobjectmanagerclient\/oninterfaceproxysignal(flags:handler:)]."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that all callbacks and signals are emitted in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"thread-default main context (see","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.MainContext.push_thread_default"},{"text":"]) that the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDBusObjectManagerClient"},{"type":"text","text":" object was constructed in. Additionally, the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"[class","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectProxy","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":"] and [class","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusProxy","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"] objects"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"originating from the ","type":"text"},{"code":"GDBusObjectManagerClient","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" object will be created in","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the same context and, consequently, will deliver signals in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"same main loop."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" type acts as a lightweight Swift reference to an underlying ","type":"text"},{"code":"GDBusObjectManagerClient","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" instance.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It exposes methods that can operate on this data type through ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientProtocol"},{"text":" conformance.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Use "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" only as an ","type":"text"},{"code":"unowned","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" reference to an existing ","type":"text"},{"code":"GDBusObjectManagerClient","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" instance.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClient","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" (instead of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef"},{"type":"text","text":") if you want to use Automatic Reference Counting for memory management of the underlying "},{"code":"GDBusObjectManagerClient","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" instance.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","style":"note"}]}],"references":{"doc://GIO/10GLibObject0B8ProtocolP":{"title":"GLibObject.ObjectProtocol","type":"unresolvable","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/10GLibObject0B8ProtocolP"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/DBusObjectManagerProtocol":{"fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"DBusObjectManagerProtocol"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/dbusobjectmanagerprotocol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerProtocol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"DBusObjectManagerProtocol"}],"title":"DBusObjectManagerProtocol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDBusObjectManager"},{"text":" type is the base type for service- and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"client-side implementations of the standardized"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"http:\/\/dbus.freedesktop.org\/doc\/dbus-specification.html#standard-interfaces-objectmanager","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"interface."}]},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/DBusObjectManagerClientRef/unowned(_:)":{"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/dbusobjectmanagerclientref\/unowned(_:)","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef\/unowned(_:)","title":"unowned(_:)","kind":"